<i>noun</i>: 불경 [불경], 무례 [무례] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>불경 [불경]</dt><br>
<dd>disrespect; irreverence</dd><br>
<dd>존경하는 태도를 보여야 할 자리에서 무례함.</dd><br>
<dd>The attitude of being disrespectful in a situation in which one should act respectfully.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>무례 [무례]</dt><br>
<dd>rudeness; disrespect</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동에 예의가 없음.</dd><br>
<dd>The quality of having no manners in one's words or behavior.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>